strapline.value: Join our Visual Designer Monika Koziol who will be speaking at the Front-end London meetup about the importance of teamwork

value.text:
Teamwork, love it or hate but no modern web application has been built by a single person. This talk will be about the benefits of designing component based UIs, lean methods, kanban and working in cross-functional and collocated teams. All from designer perspective. Ranj added this


When: Thursday 30th June, 19:00 – 21:30

Where: [Made by Many, London](https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/Made+by+Many/@51.5324355,-0.1016787,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x48761b5e9962443f:0xe79a8a7cecb49c95!8m2!3d51.5324355!4d-0.09949)
